--- !u!114 &960923034062411210
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 7345706801918351265}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7adeecd4684c07f4fb3b59c542de96d3, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Interactions
  BarkBalloon: {fileID: 1244846301120538518}
  barkTextField: {fileID: 3004534396181314529}
  texts:
  - "You're finally here\u2014good! We have a situation and it's\u2014it's bad."
  - "Those things? Mutated catnip. The cats can\u2019t resist them\u2014and when
    we look at them, they panic."
  - The cats will become agressive if you look directly to their catnip.
  - But will calm down if you stop looking at it.
  - "Don\u2019t blame them, alright? They\u2019re not the problem."
  - "And be careful! They\u2019re scared, not angry\u2026 well\u2014mostly not angry."
  - "Use the gravity tool, grab the artifacts, bring them here\u2014quickly, please."
  - Put the artifacts in this platform to deactivate them.
  - Put the artifacts on this platform to my left! When all of them are deactivated,
    the cats will be safe.
  audioClips:
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: eb5c1b551931a4148b7346546f3171be, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: afc531fb0b9bb5845be98d14b0e9d484, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7a6a7686ad4ba774cb5001a88acf6538, type: 3}
